e9><eC>me </eC></e9>what <e9><eC>I </eC></e9>thought of the President 's speech . '' <br><blue>12</blue>This document is based exclusively on the content and behavior of selected foreign public media . <br><blue>13</blue>It is issued without coordination with other <e9>U.S. </e9>Government components . <br></div>
